import React from 'react'
import { Card, Icon, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const RestaurantCard = (props) => (
  <Card>
    <Image src='/mcd.png' wrapped ui={false} />
    <Card.Content>
      <Card.Header>{props.name}</Card.Header>
    </Card.Content>
    <Card.Content extra>
        {props.promo}
    </Card.Content>
  </Card>
)

export default RestaurantCard
